ex.php?topic=94600.msg878385#msg878385" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878385#msg878385</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">共同点&nbsp; 11</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878409#msg878409" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878409#msg878409</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">不同点&nbsp; 12</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878427#msg878427" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878427#msg878427</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">冬夏淑女，萨莉莎和茉莉&nbsp; 12</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878618#msg878618" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878618#msg878618</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">冬夏女王，泰坦尼亚和玛布&nbsp; 16</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878933#msg878933" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg878933#msg878933</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">寒冬夫人与盛夏夫人&nbsp; 20</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg881056#msg881056" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg881056#msg881056</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">盛夏骑士和寒冬骑士，菲克斯和哈利&nbsp; 20</span><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg881188#msg881188" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=94600.msg881188#msg881188</a><br><br><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size">其他注意点&nbsp; 26</span><br><a href="http